data.message: Fix Intersphere Unsplash images not showing: Root cause: UNSPLASH_ACCESS_KEY not set in Render dashboard. Added key to local api/.env and guided user to add to Render. Images now working. Trade-off: adds latency on first topic load, but cached permanently after.
data.task: Fix Intersphere Unsplash images not showing
data.outcome: Root cause: UNSPLASH_ACCESS_KEY not set in Render dashboard. Added key to local api/.env and guided user to add to Render. Images now working. Trade-off: adds latency on first topic load, but cached permanently after.
